   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Arousyag Campaign to Support Women &amp; LGBT People</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Arousyag campaign, a brainchild of a few UK-based individuals, unites two human rights charities, the Women&apos;s Resource Center (WRC) &amp; Pink Armenia (Pink), who are pioneers in supporting the rights of women, young girls and LGBT citizens in Armenia. The outbreak of the COVID-19 pandemic has created unprecedented difficulties for these marginalised groups, isolating and depriving them of the crucial social, psychological, legal and medical support offered by these two respected NGOs.</narrative>
  </description>
